translations: 快步进行曲；轻快的舞步

sentences.sentence: A few minutes passed and again the voice of the Manager called, "Quickstep!"
sentences.translation: 几分钟过去了，经理又喊了一声：“快步走！”

sentences.sentence: Traditional dances include the waltz quickstep tango foxtrot and so on.
sentences.translation: 传统舞蹈包括华尔兹、快步舞、探戈、狐步舞等等。

sentences.sentence: We did all of the ballroom dances, quickstep, fox-trot, tango and waltz.
sentences.translation: 我们做所有的舞厅舞，快步，狐小跑，探戈舞和华尔兹。
